<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>ANTILOCK BRAKES/TRACTION CONTROL: MERITOR WABCO WITH "D" VERSION ECU - AUTOMATIC TRACTION CONTROL (ATC) -
        DEEP SNOW AND MUD SWITCH
    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="operate" graphiccount="1">
        <title>DEEP SNOW AND MUD SWITCH</title>
        <para>A deep snow and mud option switch is included with ATC. This function increases available traction on
            extra soft surfaces like snow, mud or gravel, by slightly increasing the permissible wheel spin.
        </para>
        <para>Drivers use a deep snow and mud switch to select this feature. When this function is in use, the ATC
            indicator lamp blinks continuously (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f0403714">Figure 14</hotlnk>).
        </para>
        <figure id="f0403714" figsize="pg-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figg04/g0403714.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="312px"
                     scalefitheight="352px"/>
            <caption>Figure 14. ABS Indicator Lamp Blinks Continuously</caption>
        </figure>
        <para>Here's how the Deep Snow and Mud feature works:</para>
        <table id="t0403702" frame="all">
            <title>Deep Snow and Mud Feature Operation</title>
            <tgroup cols="4" colsep="1" rowsep="1">
                <colspec colwidth="2.11in"/>
                <colspec colwidth="2.04in"/>
                <colspec colname="col3" colwidth="1.11in"/>
                <colspec colname="col4" colwidth="1.16in"/>
                <spanspec namest="col3" nameend="col4" spanname="3to4"/>
                <thead>
                    <row>
                        <entry morerows="1" align="center">
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">Driver Action</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry morerows="1" align="center">
                            <para>System Response</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colspan="2" spanname="3to4" align="center">
                            <para>Function</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry>
                            <para>-</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>-</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>Active</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>Not Active</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <row>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Press deep snow and mud switch</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>ATC lamp blinks continuously</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>X</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry></entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Press switch again</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>ATC lamp stops blinking</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry></entry>
                        <entry colname="col4" align="center">
                            <para>X</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                </tbody>
            </tgroup>
        </table>
        <specpara>
            <note>
                <para>Turning off the ignition will also deactivate the deep snow and mud feature.</para>
            </note>
        </specpara>
    </svcproc>
